Serializable, org.apache.bcel.Constants
public class UninitializedObjectType
extends org.apache.bcel.generic.ReferenceType
implements org.apache.bcel.Constants

This class represents an uninitialized object type; see The Java Virtual Machine Specification, Second Edition, page 147: 4.9.4 for more details. WARNING! These classes are a fork of the bcel verifier.
